data.meta_description: Juana Enríquez CASTILLE was born in the year 1425 in Torrelobatón, Valladolid, Castilla-Leon, Spain, daughter of Bernhard Frederik Enriquez MENDOZA and Mariana of TOLEDO., they gave birth to 1 child. She died on February 13, 1468 in Tarragona, Catalonia, Spain. This information is part of Pop Oswald Tree by Peter John Oswald on Genealogy Online.
